{"tid":165000,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂 Switch 過熱 microSD 溶化辣親手","createTime":"2017-03-21T04:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T23:18:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"434fa74bc11aff8ba9a10fae45eb7f9ab568d3ac","tid":165000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b16fa41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 玩生活‧樂科技 17 March, 2017<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/17/microsd-melted-in-nintendo-switch/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2Fmicrosd-melted-in-nintendo-switch%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8356095e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/17/microsd-melted-in-nintendo-switch/game-channel/</a><br />\n唐美鳳<br />\n由於內置記憶體容量只得 32GB，任天堂 Switch 的玩家們都要額外購買 microSD 增加儲存空間。不過原來選購 microSD 都大有學問，日前外國有玩家就因此發生意外，還被 microSD 灼傷手指。至於是因為任天堂 Switch 還是 microSD 卡本身出問題，至今還未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n早前一名 Switch 玩家 Sosowski 在 Twitter 向 SanDisk 投訴，指他將 128GB microSD 插入 Switch 不久就出現過熱情況。Sosowski 表示在拔出 microSD 期間，開始溶解外殼把他的手指燙傷，他的指紋甚至印到 microSD 外殼上。過往亦有 SanDisk SD 卡出現過熱的狀況，不過出現於任天堂 Switch 則相信是首次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nSanDisk 收到 Sosowski 的公開投訴後，已經聯絡了當事人安排更換和進行調查。究竟問題是出於 SanDisk 還是任天堂，可能要看看 SanDisk 和 Sosowski 會否交代調查結果了。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Twitter ＠Sosowski<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=803f8a78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁 <a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=16319f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a> <br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=65a2a69f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\nThe post 疑任天堂 Switch 過熱 microSD 溶化辣親手 appeared first on <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b16fa41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 玩生活‧樂科技."},{"pid":"612d7de1409f6b21086e8a5531513209ed3edfed","tid":165000,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"睇到topic已經知係機界原種開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08378f1303bd18d4656d58c415c0a9de85bef615","tid":165000,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"switch唔係行遊戲卡？"},{"pid":"406648b5ffd3c846fda0d991cbec6a3ae597d1e1","tid":165000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>switch唔係行遊戲卡？</blockquote><br />\n外加記憶卡"},{"pid":"e1c5dd00c3370deff7984ab428a7e1447ac6c2d8","tid":165000,"uid":36818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"兄弟，話左係張卡問題，唔係部機喎"},{"pid":"c388cd843c9a7d09d5ce20a6edc208f2d88082ba","tid":165000,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"原來係underwear賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553174522d291725355ef239b8e8a775db084716","tid":165000,"uid":11499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到topic已經知係機界原種開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同睇到「90後新人職場抗壓力低」<br /